'''Metal boots''' are [[armour]] pieces in ''[[RuneScape]]'' that are worn in the [[footwear slot]]. They are protective footwear that are made out of armour [[metal]]s and ''cannot'' be made with the [[Smithing]] skill. They offer more protection than most standard boots with the expense of extra weight. All metal boots (except [[White boots]] and [[Bandos boots]]) are dropped by [[Slayer]] monsters.

They come in the following types: [[Bronze boots|Bronze]], [[Iron boots|Iron]], [[Steel boots|Steel]], [[Black boots|Black]], [[Mithril boots|Mithril]], [[Adamant boots|Adamant]], [[Rune boots|Rune]], and [[Dragon boots|Dragon]]. Also, there are white boots and Bandos boots.

